org.openpnp.gui.tablemodel

Interface ColumnAlignable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlacementsHolderLocationsTableModel, PlacementsHolderPlacementsTableModel, PlacementsHolderTableModel

    public interface ColumnAlignable
    An interface for TableModels that defines how the corresponding columns of the Table should be aligned

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int CENTER
      Constant used to indicate the contents of the column should be aligned on the center

      static int RIGHT
      Constant used to indicate the contents of the column should be aligned on the right edge
